        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "破煩惱惡。",
        "translation": "It destroys the afflictions and evils.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c19_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "摧伏四魔。",
        "translation": "He destroys the four demons and subdues them.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c19_4",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "出陰界獄。",
        "translation": "He escapes the aggregates, elements, and hells.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c20_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夫所謂少欲知足者。",
        "translation": "Someone who's content with few desires wants to be content.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c21_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "正欲省其精力以辦出要耳。",
        "translation": "He wants to conserve his energy so that he can get out of the essentials.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c21_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "倘托言知足而反坐在懈怠坑中。",
        "translation": "If he pretends to be content but sits in the pit of laziness instead.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c22_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則墜落不淺矣。",
        "translation": "Then he won't fall too far down.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c22_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "故必常行精進以破見思煩惱。",
        "translation": "Therefore, you must always conduct yourself with energy to break the afflictions of views and perceptions.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c23_0",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "煩惱之魔既破。",
        "translation": "Once the demons of affliction are destroyed, then the demons of the aggregates and gods and the demons of death will all fall through.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c23_1",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "則陰魔天魔死魔皆悉摧伏。",
        "translation": "Then the aggregates demons, gods demons, and death demons will all be destroyed.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c23_2",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "而五陰十八界獄乃可出也。",
        "translation": "The five aggregates and 18 realms and hells can then be escaped.",
        "source": "X37n0672_001:0737c24_3",
        "is_bad_quality": false
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "△五多聞智慧覺。",
